{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/27756", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/27756/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/27756/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/27756/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/27756", "id": 100619791, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUxMDA2MTk3OTE=", "number": 27756, "title": "Mistaken warning when working around `E0386` restrictions regarding mutable references in immutable containers.", "user": {"login": "nathankleyn", "id": 220826, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIyMDgyNg==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/220826?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn", "html_url": "https://github.com/nathankleyn", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2015-08-12T19:43:14Z", "updated_at": "2015-08-13T08:15:39Z", "closed_at": "2015-08-13T08:15:39Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "While writing the detailed diagnostics for `E0386` (cannot assign to data in an immutable container, #24407), I came across a possible mistaken warning.\n\n`E0386` is about forbidding mutation of a mutable reference stored in an immutable container:\n\n``` rust\nlet mut x: i64 = 1;\nlet y: Box<_> = Box::new(&mut x);\n**y = 2; // error, cannot assign to data in an immutable container\n```\n\nBut if you make `y` mutable to get around this issue, you get a warning:\n\n``` rust\nlet mut x: i64 = 1;\nlet mut y: Box<_> = Box::new(&mut x); // warning, variable does not need to be mutable\n**y = 2;\n```\n\nAlthough it _is_ strictly true that I don't mutate `y` itself, that I need `y` to be `mut` to be able to mutate the members makes this warning a bit dubious.\n", "closed_by": {"login": "nathankleyn", "id": 220826, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIyMDgyNg==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/220826?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn", "html_url": "https://github.com/nathankleyn", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nathankleyn/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/27756/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/27756/timeline", "performed_via_git